OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying very
OL,6,Fwarm and humid overnight. Dry for most
OL,7,Fbut elevated thunderstorms possible by
OL,8,Fthe early hours of the morning. These
OL,9,Fcould turn gusty with hail and thunder.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FAny early morning
OL,12,Fthunderstorms will move northward.
OL,13,FAnother very hot day to come as
OL,14,Fhumidity levels remain high. Very
OL,15,Flittle cloud to start but could see
OL,16,Fsome sea fog later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
